WEBVTT

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:33.000
We went to lots of places.
We interviewed around four hundred people,

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:36.240
took photographs, spoke to them.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:41.400
Older people have so many stories, 
so many experiences,

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:45.520
we decided to capture these.

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:49.320
You must be aware that
the younger population

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:52.320
in India is estimated at about 35 crores.

00:02:52.320 --> 00:02:54.840
So today, I want to know from you,

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:57.480
what does "aging" mean to you?

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:02.640
I asked this question to Amrita Pritam,